Murray's Song  
  
  *tuning low to high:*  
  [GCECBE]  
  *tune your up to an E with the low 12th harm. tune your up to*  
  *a C with the 8th fret of the low E. tune the up to a G with the*  
  *seventh fret of the C string to the 5th fret of the now G string.*  
  
  [E----------2-0---2--2P0-----------2-0-------------2---0-2-3-5-5--2----------  
  B--2---2H3---0---3--3P0-0-----2H3---0---0-----2H3---3--------------3SL5-530-  
  G-------------------------2------------0--2---------------------2----------2  
  E----2-----2---0----0-------2-----2---0-----2-----2---0-----0--2--------0-0-  
  C-------------------------------------------------------------2-------------  
  G--2---2-----0---0--------2----2----0-----2---2-----0-----0--------0-----0-2]  
  
  *This is basically the song minus one part, which i can't figure out.*  
  *it just repeats, and ends on [X22225].*<!--n:Murray's Song:s:7269:e:1100-->
