The Impending Death of the Virgin Spirit  
  
  *This is kind of a mix between the studio version and the Windham*  
  *Hill in Concert video performance. Both performances are cool*  
  *and aren't much different, but you may notice some phrasing*  
  *discrepancies. This is basically how I play it.*  
  *BTW, this is easier than "Bricklayer", but more of a pain to get*  
  *in tune properly. It's worth it though :-)*  
  *Tuning (low to high): [C# A C# G# A E], then capo on 2nd fret*  
